{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23212.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day16.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"surround":"7003_wind","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Miss Akemi, is Kyubey...?"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime05","chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","surround":"stop","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I've already handled it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-3"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Oh, wow...@He's full of holes."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-4"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It was Kyosuke Kamijo lashing out@at her that pushed her over the edge."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]As long as that memory is gone,@she has no reason to make a contract."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes. That should be how it pans out."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Can I ask a question?"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If you can influence others as you please@by simply erasing memories at will..."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...doesn't that make your powers useful@in any situation?"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-10"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...No, it doesn't work like that."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The other party needs to clearly remember@the moment..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Basically, the \"film\" of that memory@needs to be burned into the mind."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So things that people don't want to@remember, like traumatic memories..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-14"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...can't be forcibly erased."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...I see."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Also, to be frank..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-18"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'd rather not use an ability that can@manipulate people's minds if I can help it."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...That's understandable."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]To find happiness by forgetting or@never knowing... It's cruel, in a way."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-21"},{"id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But...in this case, our efforts@will have been worth it."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104208/vo_full_909116-017-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]This time, we'll surely be able to prevent@Madoka from making a contract."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
